# Dual License

This repository contains two types of content with different licenses:

## 1. Corpus Texts (sources/ directory)

The text files in the `sources/` directory are in the **Public Domain** or have specific licenses noted in their metadata files.

### Public Domain Dedication (CC0 1.0 Universal)

To the extent possible under law, the curators of this corpus have waived all copyright and related or neighboring rights to the public domain texts contained in this corpus. This work is published from: United States.

For the full CC0 1.0 Universal license text, see:
https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

### Licensed Texts

Some texts may have specific licenses or usage restrictions. These are noted in the individual metadata files (`sources/*.meta.yaml`). Always check the metadata before using a text.

