## Attribution

When using texts from this corpus, please attribute as follows:

```
Source: Ignaria Corpus (https://github.com/flaremark/ignaria-corpus)
Text: [Title] by [Author]
Version: [corpus version]
```

## Questions

For licensing questions or permissions, please open an issue at:
https://github.com/flaremark/ignaria-corpus/issues
